{"tid":93151,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫][勵志文]俄羅斯美女下嫁毒撚","createTime":"2017-01-24T07:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T09:56:45.000Z","uid":21742,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"641ed21d764db9bf0efd4671f9999df0c1b0df8e","tid":93151,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"東歐是男人的天堂，俄羅斯也不例外，PTT上有網民發了一篇名為《俄羅斯 越看越憤怒！》的帖子，前幾張圖我們看到的是俄羅斯的美女，但最後幾張，鄉民憤怒了！大呼：「屌你老母」「佢憑乜撚野？」「呢篇一定係勵志文」等言論，直接把該帖子噓爆<br />\n我們來看下這有多讓人憤怒.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">▼俄羅斯美女，有氣質又清新，太正了！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/6FE77PJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2F6FE77PJ.jpg&h=c9c64882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/dYXkJLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FdYXkJLF.jpg&h=622b3dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/ncjnXbl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FncjnXbl.jpg&h=0414e382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/iLfxpyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FiLfxpyL.jpg&h=3c429448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/4scSmqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2F4scSmqa.jpg&h=bbea4acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">▼看到這裡，很多人都會.......</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/3WCZb8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2F3WCZb8g.jpg&h=88a2397f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">扯左！！！！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/OyQpuuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FOyQpuuZ.jpg&h=71d7c00f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">▼很多人的感受應該是這樣的......</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/32/Mama.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070110222122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F32%2FMama.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070110222122&h=38bfba1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n網路上流傳她的更多的照片~~~</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/ARMZ4CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FARMZ4CM.jpg&h=d9f7fb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/mxeHuMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FmxeHuMt.jpg&h=7e061754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/BqWKBV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FBqWKBV9.jpg&h=15b18dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/O2Hzl15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FO2Hzl15.jpg&h=0ae8d1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/LhfHHGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FLhfHHGE.jpg&h=ad05d738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/NN5Af1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FNN5Af1s.jpg&h=fdbc1838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/CHMoh12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FCHMoh12.jpg&h=e49aec9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/kLodryq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FkLodryq.jpg&h=fe54aae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/G9q4k96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FG9q4k96.jpg&h=05f80d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/eBDBXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FeBDBXH8.jpg&h=9f4457f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/sC13tyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FsC13tyX.jpg&h=e3271509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/bvNglJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FbvNglJH.jpg&h=c1d52d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/h51DC8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fh51DC8K.jpg&h=b6574e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/QVXYY4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FQVXYY4t.jpg&h=5a223fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實宅男會把到俄羅斯美女是有一定道理的~~~</span><br />\n</span><br />\n之前新聞也有報導過：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">俄羅斯美女缺男人！　《如何嫁給外國人》登暢銷書</span><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯男女比例嚴重失衡，女多男少，導致許多女性找不到老公，只好向「外」發展，《如何嫁給外國人》一書，更是在俄羅斯狂銷熱賣；甚至有議員曾提議，通過立法對「跨國婚姻」作限制。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯男女比例為1:1.2，男性約有6700多萬人，表示有1000多萬名女性找不到老公，引發一系列社會問題，像是男性沒有責任感、酗酒、脾氣不好，還有一夫多妻及「跨國婚姻」等問題激增；《如何嫁給外國人&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;101條建議》一書，更在俄羅斯熱賣。<br />\n<br />\n據美國司法部統計，近12年來，嫁給美國人成為公民並移民到美國的俄羅斯婦女有7.5萬人，平均年齡為28歲；由於外嫁的俄羅斯新娘大都受過良好教育，且年輕貌美，專家擔心將對俄整理人口素質產生負面影響，甚至有議員提議，立法限制跨國婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n但不論是哪個國家的女性，都渴望找到夢中情人，1名俄羅斯攝影師看準單身女子對愛情的渴望，請她們描繪出心中「完美男人」的樣貌並拍下來，佐以文字敘述她們的故事及期盼。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n▼俄羅斯女性描繪出心目中的「完美男人」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p1.imgs.photo.ckcdn.com/20130325/51500c97a32e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.imgs.photo.ckcdn.com%2F20130325%2F51500c97a32e8.jpg&h=43c368e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯女性心中的「完美男人」原來是這樣的.....<br />\n<br />\n那文中的宅男能把到俄羅斯美女就不意外了.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家機票都準備好了嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf542904bf4aeedf5a2eea65439f5f19d1bea1b","tid":93151,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"補番個來源: <a href=\"http://ck101.com/thread-2680396-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-2680396-1-1.html&d=rwHUzJFazYqurwARpf8t4JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1d83a4dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://ck101.com/thread-2680396-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"a903cbea144b205537a1024d4e92086c7dda217c","tid":93151,"uid":32391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"好想識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae83b08af2da711700ad30dbdd3b2b6245b8b096","tid":93151,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"這些機會.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f0edf20d6b57fe2cc25f80139a30b295646cd6","tid":93151,"uid":46669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"有無人知回左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女做人阿婆未"},{"pid":"31e398f6c9f0a83e625331de8c2c1139c425ab74","tid":93151,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人知回左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女做人阿婆未</blockquote><br />\n條仔可能戴埋帽離埋婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d21eac3ff3e75d88de0ba